\f1\b0\fs44 \cf2 1. 
\b PB Frappe
\b0  Puree 1/4 cup peanut butter with 1 cup milk. Pour some chocolate syrup into a glass; top with the peanut-butter milk. Slowly add seltzer and stir.\
2. 
\b Vietnamese Iced Coffee
\b0  Pour 3 tablespoons sweetened condensed milk over ice; stir in 1 cup cooled strong coffee.\
3. 
\b Honeydew Ice
\b0  Puree 1 cup each frozen honeydew melon and frozen diced cucumber with the juice of 1 lime and some sugar.\
4. 
\b Sake Spritzer
\b0  Combine 1 basil leaf, 6 mint leaves, 2 lemon twists, 1 orange wedge, 1/4 cup diced cucumber and 1 1/2 ounces orange liqueur in a shaker with ice; shake. Pour into a glass and top with sparkling sake.\
