\cf2 5. 
\b Peach-Ginger Iced Tea
\b0  Mash 6 canned peach halves with 1 1/2 cups of the juice, 1/3 cup sugar and 1 tablespoon grated ginger in a pitcher. Add ice and 6 cups cold English breakfast tea.\
6. 
\b Pineapple Rummy
\b0  Fill a glass partway with sparkling cider and ice. Add a shot of dark rum and a few pineapple chunks.\
7. 
\b Concord Cow
\b0  Scoop some vanilla ice cream into a glass. Mix equal parts concord grape juice and lemon-lime soda, then slowly pour over the ice cream.\
8. 
\b Real-Man's Margarita
\b0  Salt the rim of a beer mug; fill with ice. Add Mexican beer, a squeeze of lime juice, a splash of tequila and hot sauce to taste.\
